{"tid":650894,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今次呢單野應該連六月娘都唔知點幫手","createTime":"2018-05-02T17:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T16:56:32.000Z","uid":156948,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"75f58cb42db2a1e35bfbeec93b2f42f0430788fc","tid":650894,"uid":156948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"本身andrew lo自己個mock出錯題目 有人好心提吓佢 如果佢肯直接扮死狗認眼大睇過龍唔小心出錯題目嘅話而家呢一刻已經唔會再有人討論 但係呢條on9仔竟然係cliff yeung話埋佢出錯題目之後都仲要死頂 同cliff yeung互片之前唔該起吓人底 睇吓人地咩料先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前串過人地cliff yeung 人地好聲好氣廢事同你嘈你條傻閪都仲要唔知死 今次搵埋科大黎搞仲要比人出埋聲明話柒你真係柒到搵窿捐都唔撚掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上cliff yeung打滾咗咁多年都搵夠錢 唔會因為燈塔話炒佢而屈服 所以我諗andrew lo你揀錯人挑機真係可以收收皮先 呢鋪六月娘都唔會幫到你 因為件事由頭到尾都係你自己死雞撐飯蓋愈搞愈大 你都係上吓cliff啲精讀班先出黎教人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e74bf835eee2f838a9547f9fff9cdab39895f3","tid":650894,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b622e3f6dd64b751edf1b54f9039cf8dfcef703","tid":650894,"uid":1139,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T17:24:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b6afa7e54bc96b7b3e8f17e38eedac34841093a","tid":650894,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72e74bf835eee2f838a9547f9fff9cdab39895f3","tid":650894,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T17:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ce2c12b55aa407b4149490b3d5854e3707ac9c","ti